BD%E5%8A%9B%E6%98%AF%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84**%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%87%8D%E6%9E%84%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%5Cn-%20**%E5%8F%AF%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D%E7%9A%84**%EF%BC%9A%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E8%80%A6%5Cn-%20**%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8D%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84**%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A0%88%5Cn%5Cn%E8%BF%99%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%20Kecare%20%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%A0%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%5C%22%E5%A4%96%E6%8C%82%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%5C%22%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%5C%22%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%87%8D%E5%86%99%5C%22%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E3%80%82%5Cn%22%2C%22translatedMarkdown%22%3A%22%23%20About%20Kecare%3A%20Start%20Here%5Cn%5Cn%3E%20%F0%9F%92%A1%20**Before%20You%20Begin**%3A%20If%20you%20find%20any%20part%20of%20the%20documentation%20unclear%2C%20feel%20free%20to%20open%20an%20Issue%20or%20submit%20a%20PR%20to%20help%20improve%20it.%20Your%20contributions%20are%20greatly%20appreciated!%5Cn%5CnKecare%20is%20a%20generator%20framework%20designed%20for%20modern%20static%20blogs%20and%20note%20sites.%20Its%20primary%20goal%20is%20not%20to%20%5C%22create%20another%20Hexo%2C%5C%22%20but%20to%20decouple%20the%20**content%20system**%20from%20the%20**theme%2Fframework**%2C%20turning%20your%20blogging%20capabilities%20into%20%5C%22pluggable%20modules.%5C%22%5Cn%5Cn---%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Core%20Advantage%3A%20Non-Invasive%20Design%5Cn%5CnMany%20traditional%20blog%20solutions%20(like%20Hexo)%20lock%20you%20into%20a%20fixed%20ecosystem%3A%20themes%2C%20builds%2C%20plugins%2C%20directory%20structures%20are%20all%20tightly%20coupled%20to%20it.%20Changing%20the%20tech%20stack%20means%20starting%20over.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Kecare's%20Solution%5Cn%5CnThe%20core%20advantage%20of%20Kecare%20lies%20in%20its%20**non-intrusiveness**.%5Cn%5Cn%3E%20**One-sentence%20explanation**%3A%20If%20you%20are%20a%20front-end%20developer%2C%20you%20can%20directly%20%5C%22add%5C%22%20a%20blog%20system%20to%20your%20existing%20application%2C%20with%20almost%20no%20need%20to%20care%20about%20what%20technology%20stack%20the%20original%20project%20uses.%5Cn%5CnYou%20just%20need%20to%20create%20a%20%60.kecare%2F%60%20directory%20in%20your%20project%2C%20write%20the%20content%20and%20rules%20according%20to%20the%20convention%2C%20and%20Kecare%20will%20generate%20blog-related%20pages%20and%20data%20based%20on%20the%20rules%20you%20define.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Supported%20Technology%20Stacks%5Cn%5CnYour%20original%20project%20could%20be%3A%5Cn%5Cn%7C%20Type%20%7C%20Framework%20Examples%20%7C%5Cn%7C------%7C----------%7C%5Cn%7C%20Vue%20Ecosystem%20%7C%20Vue%203%2C%20Nuxt%20%7C%5Cn%7C%20React%20Ecosystem%20%7C%20React%2C%20Next.js%20%7C%5Cn%7C%20Svelte%20Ecosystem%20%7C%20Svelte%2C%20SvelteKit%20%7C%5Cn%7C%20Traditional%20SSR%20%7C%20Any%20server-side%20rendering%20framework%20%7C%5Cn%7C%20Legacy%20Projects%20%7C%20As%20long%20as%20you%20can%20integrate%20the%20generated%20results%20%7C%5Cn%5Cn**Kecare%20doesn't%20force%20you%20to%20migrate%2C%20change%20your%20architecture%2C%20or%20rewrite%20your%20pages.**%20It%20acts%20like%20an%20%5C%22external%20content%20production%20line%2C%5C%22%20attaching%20the%20blog%20system%20to%20your%20project%20in%20the%20lightest%20way%20possible.%5Cn%5Cn---%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Two%20Ways%20to%20Use%5Cn%5CnKecare%20offers%20two%20%5C%22friendly%20onboarding%20paths%5C%22%20for%20you%20to%20choose%20from%20based%20on%20your%20needs%3A%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Method%201%3A%20Default%20Theme%20(Out-of-the-Box)%5Cn%5CnIf%20you%20just%20want%20to%20have%20a%20running%2C%20aesthetically%20pleasing%2C%20and%20writable%20blog%20immediately%2C%20you%20can%20directly%20use%20the%20**default%20theme**%20provided%20by%20the%20official.%5Cn%5Cn%7C%20Feature%20%7C%20Description%20%7C%5Cn%7C------%7C------%7C%5Cn%7C%20Tech%20Stack%20%7C%20Nuxt%20%2B%20Vue%203%20%7C%5Cn%7C%20Target%20Audience%20%7C%20Users%20who%20want%20to%20start%20writing%20quickly%20and%20get%20their%20blog%20up%20and%20running%20%7C%5Cn%7C%20Difficulty%20Level%20%7C%20Low%2C%20almost%20no%20need%20to%20understand%20Kecare's%20internal%20details%20%7C%5Cn%7C%20Startup%20Method%20%7C%20Place%20the%20%60.kecare%2F%60%20content%20as%20per%20the%20documentation%20and%20run%20the%20command%20%7C%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Method%202%3A%20Custom%20Themes%20(True%20Non-Intrusive%20Capability)%5Cn%5CnIf%20you%20value%20the%20freedom%20of%20being%20%5C%22technology%20stack%20agnostic%2C%5C%22%20the%20custom%20theme%20route%20is%20designed%20for%20you.%5Cn%5CnYou%20can%3A%5Cn%5Cn1.%20**Create%20a%20%60.kecare%2F%60%20directory%20in%20any%20tech%20stack%2Fframework**%5Cn2.%20**Define%20generation%20rules%20in%20your%20preferred%20way**%20(e.g.%2C%20how%20articles%20are%20converted%20to%20HTML%2C%20how%20routing%20data%20is%20generated%2C%20how%20menu%20data%20is%20generated%2C%20etc.)%5Cn3.%20**Let%20Kecare%20output%20consumable%20content%20artifacts%20for%20your%20project**%20(e.g.%2C%20structured%20data%2C%20static%20page%20fragments%2C%20resource%20indexes%2C%20etc.)%5Cn%5CnThen%20your%20project%20only%20needs%20to%20do%20one%20thing%3A%5Cn%5Cn%3E%20**By%20integrating%20Kecare's%20output%20for%20rendering%20(or%20directly%20publishing%20it)%2C%20you%20have%20completed%20a%20set%20of%20%5C%22external%20blog%20system%5C%22.**%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Summary%5Cn%5CnKecare's%20Design%20Philosophy%3A%5Cn%5Cn-%20**Blogging%20capability%20is%20additional**%3A%20No%20need%20to%20refactor%20existing%20projects%5Cn-%20**Portable**%3A%20Content%20is%20decoupled%20from%20themes%5Cn-%20**Theme-agnostic**%3A%20Supports%20any%20technology%20stack%5Cn%5CnThis%20is%20the%20ideal%20state%20of%20Kecare%3A%20making%20the%20blog%20system%20an%20%5C%22add-on%20module%5C%22%20for%20your%20project%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20reason%20to%20%5C%22rewrite%20everything%20from%20scratch.%5C%22%22%7D`
